name: Rochelle Pangilinan
description: '''Rochelle Pangilinan-Solinap''' (born May 23, 1982) is a Filipino actress, dancer and singer. She was part of the original lineup of the [[SexBomb Girls]], a dance group that gained popularity through the variety show ''[[Eat Bulaga!]]''. In 2007, she briefly rebranded as a rap artist under the name '''RoC'''.
